v#00681441 Android Lab 4: Article Search App

Submitted by Michael Oyetibo.

The Article Search App displays articles using an API. It allows you to click into each article and read the material.

Time spent: 1.5 hours total.

Required Features:
The following needed functionality has been completed:

 The primary criteria for this project will allow a user to see a list of article abstracts, together with the article title, description, and media photo.
 When they tap on a certain article, it will take them to a details screen that has the same information as the article's author.
Stretch Features
 For stretch features, our application's UI will be changed with fonts and ConstraintLayout for each screen.
